Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.58,0:00:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,OVERCAST
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Regardless of how she came\Nto the conclusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact remains\Nthis woman knows the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If she gives this information\Nto the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't take them very long\Nto figure out that Kira is actually me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to eliminate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But the more I think about it,\Nthe more your theory makes sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't waste any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to start investigating it\Nright away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really? Do you mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, have you told anyone else about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're the first person I've told.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky.\NBut how will you get rid of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you can do it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Well, you have a gift\Nfor stating the obvious, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, aren't you bold?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please tell me the date and time\Nof the bus-jacking incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was December 20th,\Nin front of Asagao Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At 11:02 a.m., bound for Space Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,December 20th, and they were\Non their way to Space Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,SHOKO MAKI\NSUICIDE JANUARY 1, 2007
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Commits suicide in such a way\Nthat nobody will be inconvenienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and her body will not be discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dies by implementing this plan\Nwithin 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] This way,\Nno one will find her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if they do, they'll just assume
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that the death of her fiancé\Ndrove her to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What's so funny, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk laughs maniacally]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I apologize for questioning\Nall of you like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm afraid I had no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've determined that Kira is not among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[all sighing in relief]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, how can you be certain\Nthat we're all innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to be honest, from the beginning,\NI set a number of traps
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that would reveal if any of you was Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But after speaking with you one on one,\NI don't feel the need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[all sighing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable. He tells us\Nto turn off our cellphones...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just about finished here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the key, so let yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Watari is on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:03:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to report this incident\Nto my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's okay with you, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it's all the same,\NI think I'd like to report it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And after talking to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided that it would be best\Nto do it as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Uh, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ten seconds until 1:15…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to admit,\NI'd really love to see how she dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't be caught\Nfollowing her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, hurry to your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[ticking]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[clock ticking]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] Kira will definitely be caught.\NDon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[ticking]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NIt should have happened already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't make sense.\NI don't understand why she's not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,SUICIDE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had no problems making people\Nkill themselves in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All I had to do is\Nwrite the word "suicide."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The criminals I tested it on\Nall hung themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly when I specified.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My experiments indicate\Nthat in a situation like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be able to control\Na person's actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Ryuk…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He laughed just like that\Nwhen I was writing in the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] And that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember thinking it was bizarre\Nhow he laughed when I asked for her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, he's reacted the same way\Nevery time her name comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,An alias!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen,\Nit's an honor to meet all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This person is Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. What about your usual outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I dressed like that, I'd be announcing\Nto the world that I am Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it takes to give away\Nthe location of our headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinarily, I would never show my face\Nto any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that I'm here is proof\Nthat you've won Ryuzaki's trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,\NI do feel honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[nervous laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I've brought those items\Nyou requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please pass them out\Nto everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Gentlemen,\Nthese are your new police IDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-[all] Huh?\N-But what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] She used an alias,\Nthat has to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ryuk knew all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He could see her real name with his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he wouldn't stop laughing.\NI should've known.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been overly cautious\Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It makes a lot of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She believes that Raye died\Nbecause he showed his ID to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, of course she'd be careful\Nnot to reveal her own identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be almost impossible\Nto ask for her real name
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing she gave me an alias\Nthe first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm too persistent,\Nshe'll get suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks suspicious that I even knew\Nshe was using an alias.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-I should probably be getting back soon.\N-Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone from the Task Force\Nmight be back there by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Oh, yeah, you could be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's cross our fingers\Nand hope someone's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! I'm running out of options here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stop this before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. What if my father calls back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I already promised her\Nthat I'd let her talk to him if he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If this phone rings, it's all over for me.\NWhat am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is crazy. All I have to do\Nis turn my cellphone off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone beeps]\N-[Light] Problem solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what needs to be done.\NJust find out her real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Her purse, her pockets...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got to have a driver's license
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,or some sort of personal identification\Non her somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a woman, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose if I had to, I could use force.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, the last thing I want to do\Nis make a scene in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get her somewhere isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But where?\NAnd what explanation could I give her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It would never work. She's too careful.\NI need a better approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to convince her\Nto give me her real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Light, you know,\Nthat deal I mentioned is still open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like putting on contact lenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely painless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Would I be willing to give up half my life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,just so I can learn\Nthis woman's real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's not even worth considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now quit wasting my time.\NJust shut your mouth, Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, do you still have business\Nat the police station then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to go there by myself,\Nif you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Soichiro] Our names and ranks are false.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Why did you give us fake IDs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, Kira requires\Na name and a face to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[L slurps, gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We will confront him\Nwith that premise in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think it should be obvious why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but of all people,\Nthe police shouldn't use fake IDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. What choice do we really have,\Ngiven the capabilities of our enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're working on this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're going to need\Nall the protection one can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be foolish not to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah. You've got a good point.\N-Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, any time you're in a situation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,where you have to give out your name\Nto a stranger,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,make sure to use the name\Nfrom your fake ID. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hmm.\N-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And be careful not to take them out while\Nin the presence of other police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I don't need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That could cause problems for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-I understand.\N-[men grunting in approval]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Very well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to request\Nthat you wear these at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, belts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one has a transmitter\Nhidden in the buckle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This will allow Ryuzaki\Nto monitor your whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you press the buckle\Ntwice like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...my cellphone will ring,\Ndisplaying your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll call you back immediately,\Nbut you won't see my number displayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the morning, all of you will go\Nto the police station as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, later on in the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll use this method to confirm the name\Nof Ryuzaki's hotel and his room number.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use this for emergencies as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! This is totally cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like some kind of secret agent\Ngoing after Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not the time to be fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Knock it off!\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much\Nfor everything you've done, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,After talking to you, I feel\Nmuch more confident about my theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering that Ryuk mentioned\Nthat eye deal again,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no doubt in my mind\Nthat she used an alias.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, once she goes to the police
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,with her theory about Kira\Nbeing on that bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and they look at all the people\NRaye Penber was investigating,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't take them long to zero in on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, she's leaving. So now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got about five minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,before that woman\Ngets to police headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I need her real name,\Nand I don't have much time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] If this woman makes it\Nto the police station
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and someone from the Task Force\Nhas returned by then,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll all be over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to find out her real name\Nand eliminate her quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Only three minutes left\Nuntil she reaches the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something\Nthat I should probably tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, it'll be impossible for you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to contact anyone\Nfrom the Task Force directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That's right.\NKeep the conversation going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to find something\Nthat she can latch onto and I've got her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Once she's comfortable,\Nthen I can get her real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't contact anyone? But why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you think it odd that there\Nwas no one at Task Force headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I did find it a bit strange,\Nbut I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Task Force has been organized\Nso that its members can't be identified
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,if nobody on the outside knows\Nwho's in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If the members' names\Nwere ever made public
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or the structure of the Task Force\Nwas revealed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd likely see another tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,along the lines of the one\Nthat claimed your fiancé's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That's why you were told earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that no one was\Nat Task Force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm trying to say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll never be able to talk to someone\Ndirectly from the Task Force
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because the police simply won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty clever. I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is supposed to be a secret,\Nthen how do you know so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I spoke too soon. She's sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. You leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm actually a member\Nof the Task Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, you're telling me\Nthat you're an agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. L is currently in charge\Nof the Task Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's leading our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. To be honest,\NI already suspected that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He was concerned that the Task Force\Nhad become too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Many detectives had quit,\Nfearing for their lives. And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,despite the fact\Nthat I'm a high school student,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,he brought me on board\Nto help out with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I've helped them solve cases\Nin the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, L trusts you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go to Task Force headquarters\Nwhenever it suits me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm allowed to investigate freely\Nas I see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, these days, the Task Force\Nis made up of a chosen few,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,an elite group of people\Nhandpicked for the job by L.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All are highly skilled, well respected,\Nand above all, trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for explaining.\NBut just to be safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to try and visit\Nthe Task Force headquarters again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I just told you.\NThey won't let you talk to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:15:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] I know, but I was hoping\NI could speak with L directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and come to think of it,\Nwho's at the police station right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, no one's there at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We need someone there at all times.\NWork in shifts if you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. Aizawa,\NI'll put you in charge of that for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. I'm on my way.\NWon't take me long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Maki, please wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's literally impossible to meet L.\NThis is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think there's a chance\Nthat he'll meet with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] Although the only contact\NI've had with him
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,was following orders through a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He might remember who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I worked under him\Nin a case in the US about two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious? You worked under L?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I didn't tell you this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,up until three months ago,\NI worked as an FBI agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it. Finally something I can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I shouldn't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I noticed early on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that your investigative skills\Nwere far beyond those of an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very cautious
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and you seem to have a gift\Nfor getting to the heart of the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could, I'd like to learn from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One lie after another.\NYou make it look easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning, I knew I had\Nto do things outside the regular channels
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because from my perspective,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,both the police and the members\Nof the Task Force were suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm certain that I can trust L.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's unrealistic,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think that if I go to headquarters\Nand I give them my name,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a chance that they'll let me\Nspeak with him directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the only person you could trust\Nwith this info was L, then why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I was upset\Nthat they wouldn't allow me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to see anyone from the Task Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you came along,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,claiming to be the son\Nof the lead detective and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] I'll be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you remind me of L.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something about you\Nthat's just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Will you investigate this case with me?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to come work with us\Nas part of the Task Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We could use your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] As I'm sure you know,\Nnot just anyone can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I know this is sudden\Nbut the team needs people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You could be doing so much more\Nthan gathering information on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have all the experience\Nas an FBI agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more talented\Nthan most of the detectives
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,currently on the Task Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And L obviously trusted you in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be that difficult\Nfor you to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All you'd need\Nis some valid identification,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a recommendation\Nfrom a current Task Force member,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and, of course,\Nyou'd need to get L's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to join the Task Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but think\Nthat it must be fate that I met you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to be the one to recommend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-I guess I got a little bit too excited.\N-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, even if you acted\Nas a consultant on this investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you have personal obligations\Nto attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention the fact\Nthat you live in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. Before all this happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd continue living in America\Nwith my fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd planned on getting married\Nin the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But now he's gone,\Nso I'm not sure what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I've come this far.\NAll she needs is a little encouragement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're young and beautiful,\Nand you've got your life ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why put it all in danger for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Now that Raye's gone,\NI've got nothing to lose anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to catch Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about anything else.\NIt's all I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me investigate this case\Nwith you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk laughs maniacally]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to see some form\Nof identification before we proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, um...\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the name\NI gave you earlier, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it wasn't actually my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm impressed\Nby how incredibly thorough you've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've stayed one step ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I suppose that's just further proof\Nof your capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So will a Japanese driver's license\Ndo the trick then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,NAOMI MISORA\NDATE OF BIRTH: 2/11/1979
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,NAOMI MISORA\NSUICIDE 1/1/2007
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, so, if you don't mind my asking,\Nwhy do you keep checking your watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's because…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ticking]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
